Package: piMIMIC
Type: Package
Title: Product of Indicators (PI) for MIMIC Models in DIF Detection, using SEM
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Cesar", "Merino-Soto", email = "sikayax@yahoo.com.ar", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides functions to analyze differential item functioning (DIF) using
    the Multiple Indicators Multiple Causes (MIMIC) framework. The piRFA function includes 
    likelihood ratio and Score tests for global, uniform, and non-uniform DIF detection, 
    as well effect sizes estimation through a fixed-to-zero parameter release strategy, and 
    squared-R differences. The implementation follows the conceptual work of Kolbe and 
    Jorgensen, and utilizes functions from the 'lavaan' and 'scripty' packages, among others.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
